3. Creatinine (CRE)> 1.5 Ã— ULN
4. Prothrombin time (PT) and international normalized ratio (INR) > 1.5 Ã— ULN. Or activated partial thromboplastin time (aPTT) > 1.5 Ã— ULN. Unless the subject had received anticoagulant treatment
